* ============================================================
* HARVEST TOP SHAKEDOWN
* ============================================================
* Purpose:
*   Flush newly harvested command/reference/regression changes through
*   a single top-layer proof path.
*
* Current coverage:
*   1. REGRESSION launcher surface
*   2. SECURITY role/session + assignment surface
*   3. Holiday/demo command usage surfaces
*   4. Curated non-destructive runtime smoke
*   5. x64 widened metrics/matrix boundary proof
*
* Rule:
*   Child regressions must bootstrap their own environment.
* ============================================================

SET ECHO ON

ECHO ============================================================
ECHO HARVEST TOP SHAKEDOWN
ECHO ============================================================

DO ..\x64

ECHO .
ECHO STEP 1: Launcher inventory
REGRESSION LIST
REGRESSION SHOW NONDESTRUCTIVE
REGRESSION SHOW X64_METRICS
REGRESSION SHOW HARVEST

ECHO .
ECHO STEP 2: Role / assignment surface
SECURITY LOGIN DEVELOPER AS Derald
SECURITY WHOAMI
SECURITY ASSIGNMENTS
SECURITY LOGOUT

ECHO .
ECHO STEP 3: Holiday/demo usage contracts
CHRISTMAS USAGE
HANUKKAH USAGE

ECHO .
ECHO STEP 4: Curated non-destructive smoke
REGRESSION RUN NONDESTRUCTIVE

ECHO .
ECHO STEP 5: x64 widened metrics proof
REGRESSION RUN X64_METRICS

ECHO .
ECHO ============================================================
ECHO HARVEST TOP SHAKEDOWN DONE
ECHO ============================================================
